      "instruction": "<p>Once the onion is starting to soften, add your <strong>lamb mince </strong>to the pan and cook for 3-4 min or until beginning to brown, breaking it up with a wooden spoon as you go</p><p>Sprinkle in your<strong> chicken stock mix</strong> and add your <strong>tomato paste</strong></p>",
